metadata.name: Immutable Serpenti
metadata.description: The signature snake style of Sazingg is captured in these serpenti earrings. The striking blue sapphire pavé and the sleek coil shape is distinctive and intricate. The meticulously crafted design and eyes of the snake are unique traits to this serpenti style. 925 Silver Snake Earrings with Blue Sapphire, Green Sapphire, or Rubie pavé (0.86 cts). Size 41mm.

attributes.value: 925 Silver Snake Earrings, Blue Sapphire pavé (0.86 cts), Green Sapphire pavé (0.86 cts), Rubie pavé (0.86 cts)
